veryEADP 3080 - Leadership and Organizational BehaviorPADM 3410 - Financial Aspects of GovernmentNoteThe remaining 6 hours may be chosen from any EADP-prefix course (except EADP 4080 , EADP 4800   and EADP 4810 ).       Return to: Majors, minors, certificates Back to Top | Print-Friendly Page Add to My Catalog               All catalogs © 2017 University of North Texas. Powered by the Acalog\u2122 Academic Catalog Management System\u2122 (ACMS\u2122).   Mobile Site.      
